	<phrase id="35" desc="">
		<original>
			Colossians 1:6, 23: The known world was evangelized by 61 A.D., in a generation! Paul is in prison when he writes Colossians — Acts 28. Therefore, Jesus' vision became a reality — "the evangelization of the nations in a generation!"
		</original>
		<translated>
			歌罗西书 1:6， 23: 公元61年， 福音在一代已经传到了全世界。 写歌罗西书时， 保罗在监狱里（使徒行传 28）。 因此， 耶稣的梦想成为了现实。 福音在一代内就传到了全世界。 
		</translated>
		<change bold="true" italic="false" modal="true" scripturekey="colossians-1-6">
			<original>
				1:6
			</original>
			<translated>
